      "writtenOn": "2026-06-09T03:58:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t believe the above is accurate.  Even if it is, we should rely on appropriate return codes.\n\nYOu might want to look at how async operations are done.  result codes aren\u0027t set until after the initial method has completed.",
